.Sh NAME
.Nm xf-gc
.Nd XF garbage-collection and cleanup support
.Sh DESCRIPTION
XF includes a GC and cleanup layer used by runtime values and VM-managed objects.
The source tree exposes GC statistics and threshold checks, indicating an explicit memory-management subsystem rather than ad hoc freeing alone.
